data.title: Czech New Wave
data.meta_description: Czech New Wave  - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. In the 1960s, political liberalization in Czechoslovakia fostered in a wave of progressive filmmaking. The cinema of this time shows a society reviewing its past and taking steps towards its future. It was led by fresh faces, inspired older generations, and ignited the desire to reform among the people, before it all fell apart a few years later.
